      <title>评分标准</title>
      <link href="/blog/yu-yin/yu-yin-ping-ce/ping-fen-biao-zhun/"/>
      <url>/blog/yu-yin/yu-yin-ping-ce/ping-fen-biao-zhun/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="评分标准"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#评分标准"></a> 评分标准</h1><h2 id="考纲"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#考纲"></a> 考纲</h2><ul><li><a href="http://www.neea.edu.cn/res/Home/1901/d15ec0514666ac280810099f9595b557.pdf">普通高等学校招生全国统一考试大纲-2019</a><ul><li>基本读音：辅音连缀、成音节、单词重音</li><li>连读、失去爆破、弱读、同化</li><li>意群与停顿、语调、句子重音、节奏</li></ul></li><li><a href="https://www.gxeea.cn/gallary/upload_images/1173_26561_1606206201913.pdf">广西高考-2021（招生考试院）</a></li><li><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%B9%BF%E4%B8%9C%E9%AB%98%E8%80%83%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD%E5%90%AC%E8%AF%B4%E8%80%83%E8%AF%95/2678957">广东高考</a></li></ul><h2 id="考察点"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#考察点"></a> 考察点</h2><table><thead><tr><th>维度分</th><th>考察点</th><th>备注</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>发音准确度</td><td>语音、声调/单词重音</td><td>与完整度无关，自由表述题中与正确答案无关<sup class="footnote-ref"><a href="#fn1" id="fnref1">[1]</a></sup></td></tr><tr><td>流畅度</td><td>语速、停顿次数、重复<sup class="footnote-ref"><a href="#fn2" id="fnref2">[2]</a></sup></td><td>与朗读的内容无关<sup class="footnote-ref"><a href="#fn1" id="fnref1:1">[1:1]</a></sup> <font style="background: green">（是否考虑回读？）</font></td></tr><tr><td>标准度/韵律</td><td>无中式口音，能灵活地运用连读、重读、失音、爆破等发音技巧，节奏良好，感情充沛<sup class="footnote-ref"><a href="#fn2" id="fnref2:1">[2:1]</a></sup><br>意群停顿、升降调、句子重音<sup class="footnote-ref"><a href="#fn1" id="fnref1:2">[1:2]</a></sup></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>完整度</td><td>朗读题：已读内容占提示文本的比例<br>自由表述题：要点覆盖率</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>语法</td><td>人称、时态、语态、单复数；<br>词汇、短语、语法结构使用<sup class="footnote-ref"><a href="#fn3" id="fnref3">[3]</a></sup></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="评分标准-2"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#评分标准-2"></a> 评分标准</h2><h3 id="选择题"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#选择题"></a> 选择题</h3><p>用户只能按事先设定的固定答案作答；只有读正确答案并且发音正确、完整，才有得分；用户回答多个选项，以后面的回答为准。<sup class="footnote-ref"><a href="#fn1" id="fnref1:3">[1:3]</a></sup></p><h3 id="总分与维度分"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#总分与维度分"></a> 总分与维度分</h3><blockquote><p>成人句子：total_score = (0.6*accuracy_score + fluency_score*0.3 + standard_score*0.1)* integrity_score/100</p><p>成人篇章：total_score = (0.5*accuracy_score + fluency_score*0.3 +standard_score*0.2)* integrity_score/100 <sup class="footnote-ref"><a href="#fn2" id="fnref2:2">[2:2]</a></sup></p></blockquote><h2 id="信度-效度"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#信度-效度"></a> 信度、效度</h2><ul><li>信度：多位专家打分，分数是否一致<ul><li>人工评分平均相关度、平均误差：计算评测员1与其它评测员的平均分的相关度、平均误差，作为评测员1的评分性能；以此类推；取多名评测员的平均作为人工评分性能</li></ul></li><li>效度：分数能否真实反映学生水平</li></ul><hr class="footnotes-sep" /><section class="footnotes"><ol class="footnotes-list"><li id="fn1" class="footnote-item"><p><a href="https://open.singsound.com/doc/engine?type=engine-en-en.sent.score">https://open.singsound.com/doc/engine?type=engine-en-en.sent.score</a> <a href="#fnref1" class="footnote-backref">↩︎</a> <a href="#fnref1:1" class="footnote-backref">↩︎</a> <a href="#fnref1:2" class="footnote-backref">↩︎</a> <a href="#fnref1:3" class="footnote-backref">↩︎</a></p></li><li id="fn2" class="footnote-item"><p><a href="https://www.xfyun.cn/doc/Ise/IseAPI.html">https://www.xfyun.cn/doc/Ise/IseAPI.html</a> <a href="#fnref2" class="footnote-backref">↩︎</a> <a href="#fnref2:1" class="footnote-backref">↩︎</a> <a href="#fnref2:2" class="footnote-backref">↩︎</a></p></li><li id="fn3" class="footnote-item"><p><a href="https://www.gxeea.cn/gallary/upload_images/1173_26561_1606206201913.pdf">广西高考-2021（招生考试院）</a> <a href="#fnref3" class="footnote-backref">↩︎</a></p></li></ol></section>]]></content>
      
      
